reviewText: It's the greatest sequel to the original film HICK TREK. It is also THE ONLY sequel to HICK TREK! I  personally think (and well I should) that it's a good film. Stupid, but good.  If you don't get it... check out "HICK TREK: The Moovie",  one of my favorite films of all time!
to long, just a lot of (DUMB) I did not like it, and would not recommend it!

this is absolutely one of the worst pieces of junk i have ever seen.  i chuckled lightly once during the film.  i almost stopped watching it several times because it was becoming excruciating. star warp'd and star wreck zone are way funnier.
